Package: mmorpg-fleet-ds
Version: __VERSION__
Section: net
Priority: optional
Architecture: amd64
Depends: docker.io | docker-ce, ca-certificates
Maintainer: Samuel <lordnns@example.com>
Homepage: https://github.com/Lordnns/MMORPG
Description: MMORPG lab — fleet DS host
 Installs the host_agent as a systemd service. The agent manages
 dedicated-server Docker containers on this host on demand from a
 remote orchestrator.
 .
 On install, pulls the DS image from GHCR.
 .
 Configure /etc/default/mmorpg-host-agent, then:
   systemctl start mmorpg-host-agent
